OL,3,CMan who met married dad-of-two for sex
OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FA hospital security guard is facing a
OL,7,Flife prison term for murdering Army
OL,8,Fveteran Paul Taylor and trying to kill
OL,9,Fanother man with a similar weapon.
OL,11,FMarried dad-of-two Mr Taylor was
OL,12,Freported missing by his wife, Maria,
OL,13,Fon 18 October last year. She had seen
OL,14,Fhim the previous evening "laughing
OL,15,Faway" watching television at their
OL,16,Ffamily home in Annan, Dumfriesshire.
