OL,3,CMan who met married dad-of-two for sex
OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FLater that night, Mr Taylor left their
OL,7,Faddress for what became a tragic fatal
OL,8,Fmeeting with teenager Jack Crawley,
OL,9,Fthen aged 19, at a secluded spot on
OL,10,Fthe outskirts of Carlisle.
OL,12,FMr Taylor was an exemplary catering
OL,13,Fmanager at the city's Cumberland
OL,14,FInfirmary, where Crawley also worked,
OL,15,Fand described as a "workaholic".
