OL,3,CMan who met married dad-of-two for sex
OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FCarlisle Crown Court heard how Mr
OL,7,FTaylor met men for sex and hid his
OL,8,Fdouble life from loved ones. He had
OL,9,Fboth bought cannabis and previously
OL,10,Fengaged in sexual activity with
OL,11,FCrawley, now 20, the pair
OL,12,Fcommunicating via dating app Grindr.
OL,14,FAfter Mr Taylor's disappearance, a
OL,15,Fhigh-profile missing person appeal and
OL,16,Fthen a murder probe were launched by
OL,17,Fdetectives. On 1 May, Crawley
OL,18,Fdisclosed to police that his body
OL,19,Fwould be found at the wildlife
OL,20,Fwatcher's haven of Finglandrigg Wood,
OL,21,Fnear Carlisle.
