OL,3,CMan who met married dad-of-two for sex
OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FOfficers found skeletal remains. His
OL,7,Fcorpse had been burned and then
OL,8,Fdragged into a shallow hollow by
OL,9,FCrawley, who used branches and sticks
OL,10,Fto hide them from view.
OL,12,FA pathologist concluded there were at
OL,13,Fleast 10 powerful blows delivered to
OL,14,FMr Taylor's face and head which, a
OL,15,Fprosecutor said, had been "completely
OL,16,Fsmashed in".
