OL,6,FAfter Mr Taylor's death, Crawley made
OL,7,Ffailed attempts to sell his Vauxhall
OL,8,FCorsa, which he later crashed and
OL,9,Fabandoned in the village of
OL,10,FLangwathby, near Penrith, on the
OL,11,Fmorning of 19 October.
OL,13,FFollowing his arrest by police, fright
OL,14,Fmasks, rope, duct tape and cable ties
OL,15,Fwere found in the bedroom of Crawley's
OL,16,FSheehan Crescent home in Carlisle.
