OL,3,CMan who met married dad-of-two for sex
OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FDetectives found Crawley had listened
OL,7,Fto a song called Romantic Homicide
OL,8,Ffive times in the hours before he
OL,9,Fkilled Mr Taylor. A download of
OL,10,FCrawley's phone showed captured images
OL,11,Fof bug sweepers and signal blockers
OL,12,Fwhile his own device was switched on
OL,13,Fto incognito mode.
OL,15,F"The prosecution case is that this was
OL,16,Fa premeditated murder," prosecutor
OL,17,FDavid McLachlan KC had told a Carlisle
OL,18,FCrown Court jury, adding "that Jack
OL,19,FCrawley had murder on his mind and
OL,20,Fcarried out his plan by killing Paul
OL,21,FTaylor".
