OL,3,CMan who met married dad-of-two for sex
OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FCrawley admitted manslaughter and
OL,7,Fdenied murder, but was convicted,
OL,8,Funanimously, by the jury of six men
OL,9,Fand six women on Monday (21 October).
OL,11,FHis claims of a carjacking gone wrong
OL,12,Fand trying to break up Mr Taylor's
OL,13,Fbody with a mallet after death and
OL,14,Fburning were dismissed by forensic
OL,15,Fevidence. He denied prosecution
OL,16,Fsuggestions that he had a fascination
OL,17,Fwith serial killers.
