OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FAfter his arrest in November on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder and release from
OL,8,Fcustody, Crawley later skipped bail
OL,9,Ffrom Carlisle.
OL,11,FHe was seen around New Year in
OL,12,FPenrith, disguised and wearing what
OL,13,Fone train station worker described as
OL,14,Fan "obviously fake" Hagrid-style beard.
OL,16,FHe travelled around Scotland before
OL,17,Fcarrying out another attack in
OL,18,Fdarkness on the outskirts of York on 5
OL,19,FJanuary. That victim was another man
OL,20,Faged in his 50s.
