OL,3,CMan who met married dad-of-two for sex
OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FThe pair had chatted on dating app
OL,7,FGrindr for the first time earlier that
OL,8,Fday, and arranged to meet in York,
OL,9,Fjust hours after Crawley had bought a
OL,10,Fclaw hammer from a city DIY shop.
OL,12,FThat second victim told a jury how
OL,13,FCrawley struck him three times with a
OL,14,Fhammer during their intimate
OL,15,Fencounter. "He didn't say anything,"
OL,16,Fhe replied when asked about Crawley's
OL,17,Fdemeanour. "It was all very, very
OL,18,Fquick. He just basically wanted to
OL,19,Fhurt me. He was aggressive."
