OL,3,CMan who met married dad-of-two for sex
OL,4,Cfound guilty of murder
OL,6,FHe was injured but managed to wrestle
OL,7,Fthe weapon from Crawley, who ran off
OL,8,Fand was later arrested in Bath.
OL,10,FCrawley denied attempting to murder
OL,11,Fthat man but was convicted,
OL,12,Funanimously, on that charge by jurors.
OL,14,FAs the verdicts were announced,
OL,15,FCrawley showed no emotion in the court
OL,16,Fdock.
OL,18,FMr Justice Goose told jurors he agreed
OL,19,Fwith their verdicts, and said he would
OL,20,Fsentence Crawley later this week.
