OL,6,F"You have now been convicted of the
OL,7,Fcounts as the jury have found, and you
OL,8,Fare to be sentenced on Wednesday at 11
OL,9,Fo'clock," he said. "You will be
OL,10,Fbrought to court for that purpose."
OL,12,FCrawley remains remanded in custody.
OL,14,FA second man on trial, 20-year-old
OL,15,FMarcus Goodfellow, of Greystone Road,
OL,16,FCarlisle, was acquitted of helping
OL,17,FCrawley dispose of the Corsa.
