OL,6,FIn a statement issued after the
OL,7,Fverdict, the family of Mr Taylor said:
OL,8,F"Our lives and world were completely
OL,9,Ftorn apart on the 18 Oct 2023 with the
OL,10,Fmurder of Paul. To us he was a husband
OL,11,Fand a dad, gentle and loving.
OL,13,F"For many years Paul worked to protect
OL,14,Fhis country giving up time being a
OL,15,Fhusband and father, now was the time
OL,16,Ffor us to be that family unit and we
OL,17,Fgrieve the loss of that and of our
OL,18,Ffuture.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
