OL,6,F"Losing Paul in these circumstances
OL,7,Fand the torment and hurt this has
OL,8,Fcaused has been horrendous and
OL,9,Findescribable.
OL,11,F"Paul will be dearly missed and he
OL,12,Fwill remain in our thoughts forever."
