OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Ian Hussey
OL,7,Fwas the senior investigating officer
OL,8,F(SIO) in the investigation. Speaking
OL,9,Fafter the verdict he said: "Paul was
OL,10,Ftragically killed after suffering an
OL,11,Fassault at the hands of Jack Crawley.
OL,12,FHe was a much-loved father, husband,
OL,13,Fbrother and friend who I know will be
OL,14,Fmissed by many.
OL,26,@qD@\OU
