OL,6,F"Crawley refused to admit to the
OL,7,Fbrutal murder of Paul instead pleading
OL,8,Fguilty to manslaughter claiming his
OL,9,Fdeath was the result of a car theft
OL,10,Fgone wrong, however after a jury heard
OL,11,Fthe evidence gathered against him,
OL,12,Fthey found him guilty of murder."
OL,14,FHe added his thanks to the jury, CPS
OL,15,Fand prosecuting counsel as well as
OL,16,Fstaff and officers at Cumbria Police
OL,17,Fand North Yorkshire Police.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
