OL,6,FDet Supt Hussey continued: "Finally, I
OL,7,Fwould like to pay tribute to Paul's
OL,8,Ffamily. They have been dignified
OL,9,Fthroughout the course of the
OL,10,Finvestigation and our thoughts remain
OL,11,Fwith them all.
OL,13,F"We know that no outcome at court will
OL,14,Fever serve as comfort to Paul's family
OL,15,Fand friends, but I do hope that the
OL,16,Fverdict today will offer a small
OL,17,Famount of closure for them, knowing
OL,18,Fthat we have brought Crawley to
OL,19,Fjustice."
